'''The Dwarf Lords''' is the sixteenth track of disc two of ''[[The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey - Original Motion Picture Soundtrack - Special Edition]]'', by [[Howard Shore]]. It is the third of four 'exclusive bonus tracks'.
